# React conventions

- Functional components only; extract hooks for reusable logic
- Feature code: `src/app/features/{feature}/` with `pages/`, `components/`, `api/`, `lib/`
- Shared UI: `src/app/shared/components/ui/` (shadcn/Radix)
- Landing page only: `src/app/pages/Home.jsx`

## Styling

- Default: Tailwind classes, slate/blue palette (see DESIGN.md)
- `paper-trading/` uses inline `style={{}}` with INK/SUB/BRAND tokens — do not migrate without explicit request
- Korean market: red = up, blue = down for prices

## API

- Use `apiClient.js` (fetch), not axios
- Feature APIs in `features/{name}/api/`
- Mock contracts in `src/mocks/` — update `types.js` when API shapes change

## Example

```jsx
// ✅ Feature component with Tailwind
export function CompanyCard({ company }) {
  return (
    <div className="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
      <h3 className="text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">{company.name}</h3>
    </div>
  );
}
```
